{"tid":1400054,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"我遊走半個英國，拍左條片","createTime":"2019-08-03T11:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:27:29.000Z","uid":148290,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"07e77f1ae0608f0a72708c7105602ff533be2730","tid":1400054,"uid":148290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:07:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟啱啱係英國畢業，係大學呢3年入邊，我走遍大部分英國嘅城市，拍左條屬於英國嘅Timelapse。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/nhQY7r7t8rA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnhQY7r7t8rA&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=59f85ef5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nhQY7r7t8rA</a> 我知道英國仲有好多好值得去嘅地方，但因為時間同金錢嘅問題我去唔哂請多多包涵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋磚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMZ4QtZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMZ4QtZ.png&h=ab7cb605&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpiEEnm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpiEEnm.png&h=7ffa7824&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOnaL2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOnaL2q.png&h=6d10f61e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5aVfW88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5aVfW88.png&h=271d8160&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8O1F8fR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8O1F8fR.png&h=d87ec544&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6FDaue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6FDaue.png&h=22145006&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBQ7OfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBQ7OfW.png&h=ba1509ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/